channel.title: Testscape (Invisibility) help
channel.description:
As some of you may know, on testscape, if another player dies, or teleports... sometimes they become invisible and the other player can't see them! this is extremly annoying when you teleport to wilderness, and something starts attacking you, but you cant fight back!!!! any help!?
Thanks
